@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="privacy-policy">
    <section>
        <h2>Data Collection and Use</h2>
        <p>We are committed to protecting your privacy. Our application does not store any personally identifiable information (PII) about our users.</p>
        <p>The email addresses collected during login are used solely for authentication and spam protection purposes. We do not use this information for marketing, nor do we share it with any third parties.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Information We Don't Collect</h2>
        <p>We intentionally do not collect or store:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Personal identification information (beyond email for authentication)</li>
            <li>Payment or financial information</li>
            <li>Location data</li>
            <li>Browser history or browsing habits</li>
            <li>Any other sensitive personal data</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not share, sell, rent, or trade any user information with third parties, including advertisers or analytics companies.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to maintain the safety of your minimal login data, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Secure transmission protocols (HTTPS)</li>
            <li>Properly hashed passwords</li>
            <li>Regular security reviews</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us.</p>
    </section>

    <p class="policy-date"><strong>Last updated:</strong> June 12, 2025</p>
</div>

<style>
    .privacy-policy {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: left;
    }
    .privacy-policy section {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .privacy-policy h2 {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        color: #2c3e50;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .privacy-policy ul {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }
    .policy-date {
        font-style: italic;
        color: #7f8c8d;
    }
</style>